title: Sexy and Sparkling After 40
description:
Attract more Love, Health, and Fun into your life! We have assembled an amazing panel of world-renowned experts who are going to share their best tips, strategies and secrets to attract more love, more vibrant health, and more fun into your life.
This series will provide you with the opportunity to make some significant changes in your life and you want to know the really cool thing about that? As you change, you will inspire your friends and loved ones to change as well, and before you know it, you are seen and admired as the leader of the sparkling woman movement in your tribe. Nice!

This event has volumes of vavoom - intimate secrets spilling out, tips you can put into practice immediately and sexy strategies to help you become the confident, loving, playful and vibrant woman you desire to be!
